\c 116 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 116\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Galata Nama Afaan Boollaa Ga'ee Deebi'ee
\m \bd 1\bd* Waaqayyo sagalee koo fi himata koo waan dhaga'eef, ani isa nan jaalladha.
\m \bd 2\bd* Inni gurra isaa gara kootti qabeera, kanaafis hamman jirutti isa nan waammadha.
\m \bd 3\bd* Futtaasaan du'aa anatti marame, waa'ee iddoo lafa jalaas yaadee dhiphinni ana irra ga'e; ani muddamaa fi gadda keessa nan lixe.
\m \bd 4\bd* Yommus, "Yaa Waaqayyo, ani sin kadhadha, lubbuu koo oolchi!" jedhee, maqaa Waaqayyoo nan waammadhe.
\m \bd 5\bd* Waaqayyo araara-qabeessaa fi qajeelaa dha, Waaqayyo keenya oo'a-qabeessas.
\m \bd 6\bd* Waaqayyo warra garraamota in eega, yeroo ani mataa buusetti inni na gargaare.
\m \bd 7\bd* Waaqayyo wanta gaarii waan siif godheef, yaa lubbuu ko, aara-galfannaa keetti deebi'i!
\m \bd 8\bd* Ati immoo yaa gooftaa, lubbuu koo du'a, ija koo imimmaan, miilla koos gufachuu oolchiteetta.
\m \bd 9\bd* Biyya warra jiraatoo keessa, ani fuula Waaqayyoo dura nan deddeebi'a.
\m \bd 10\bd* Yeroo, "Ani guddisee rakkadheera" jedhetti iyyuu, ani amantii koo nan eeggadhe.
\m \bd 11\bd* Na'ee dinqifachuu koo keessatti immoo, "Namni hundinuu sobaa dha" nan jedhe.
\m \bd 12\bd* Wanta gaarii inni anaaf godhe hundumaaf, ani Waaqayyoof maalan deebisa?
\m \bd 13\bd* Ani xoofoo fayyinaaf kenname ol nan fuudha, maqaa Waaqayyoos nan waammadha.
\m \bd 14\bd* Fuula saba isaa hundumaa duratti immoo, ani wareega koo Waaqayyoof nan baasa.
\m \bd 15\bd* Warri isaaf qulqullaa'an du'uun, ija Waaqayyoo duratti ulfaataa dha.
\m \bd 16\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo, kunoo, ani garbicha kee ti; ani garbicha kee, ilma garbittii keetii ti, ati hidhaa koo hiikteetta.
\m \bd 17\bd* Ani aarsaa galataa siif nan dhi'eessa, maqaa Waaqayyoos nan waammadha.
\m \bd 18\bd* Fuula saba isaa hundumaa duratti immoo, ani wareega koo Waaqayyoof nan baasa.
\m \bd 19\bd* Kanas oobdii mana Waaqayyoo keessatti, si keessatti yaa Yerusaalem nan baasa. Waaqayyoon jajadhaa!
\b 
